BirdNet-Behavior: tomtom215
  A Rust rewrite of BirdNET-Pi with DuckDB behavioral analytics.

This project is derived from and inspired by the following upstream works,
all licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0:

  BirdNET-Lite: K. Lisa Yang Center for Conservation Bioacoustics -
  Cornell Lab of Ornithology, Cornell University

  BirdNET-Pi (original): Patrick McGuire (mcguirepr89)
    https://github.com/mcguirepr89/BirdNET-Pi

  BirdNET-Pi (Nachtzuster's fork): Nachtzuster
    https://github.com/Nachtzuster/BirdNET-Pi

  BirdNET-Pi (tomtom215's fork): tomtom215
    https://github.com/tomtom215/BirdNET-Pi

